NAME
    variance - calculate the variance of a sample 
 
SYNOPSIS
    #include <acme.h>
    static inherit AcmeStat;
    #include AcmeStatInc
 
    float variance( float *sample );
 
DESCRIPTION
    Returns the variance of a sample.
 
EXAMPLE
    variance( ({ 1, 2, 3, 4, 5 }) ) -> 2.5
 
SEE_ALSO
    deviation(A), standard_deviation(A)
 
LAST MODIFIED                               
    980502 Devo
